              <!-- <div class="pb-48"><Countdown /></div> -->
              <h1
                class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-gray-900 sm:text-6xl"
              >
                Lone Peak Chevaliers
              </h1>
              <p
                class="relative mt-6 text-lg leading-8 text-gray-600 sm:max-w-md lg:max-w-none"
              >
                The Lone Peak Drill Team, also known as the Chevaliers, is a
                UHSAA sanctioned competitive dance sport at Lone Peak High
                School . They are elite representatives of the school who are
                meant to foster school spirit and pride. Our dancers dedicate
                many hours to practices, halftime performances and competitions,
                requiring high levels of responsibility and motivation.
              </p>
            </div>
            <div
              class="mt-14 flex justify-end gap-8 sm:-mt-44 sm:justify-start sm:pl-20 lg:mt-0 lg:pl-0"
            >
